ğŸ• SliceCraft: Custom Pizza Builder App
A full-stack web application for building custom pizzas with real-time inventory tracking, admin and user dashboards, transaction screenshot verification, and smart stock alerting.

Built with React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

ğŸš€ Features
ğŸ” Authentication & Authorization
Role-based login system (Admin & User)

JWT-secured login and registration

Passwords are hashed using bcrypt

ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ³ User Dashboard
Browse available pizza varieties

Build your custom pizza:

Choose Pizza Base (5 options)

Select Sauce (5 options)

Pick Cheese Type

Add Veggies (multi-select)

Optional Meats

Upload screenshot of transaction for order verification

Track order status: Order Received, In Kitchen, Sent to Delivery

ğŸ› ï¸ Admin Dashboard
View all orders and their status

Change status of any order

Upload and manage inventory:

Pizza base, sauce, cheese, veggies, meat

Monitor stock levels in real-time

ğŸ“¦ Inventory Management
Automatically updates stock quantities when orders are placed

Inventory data shown in admin dashboard

Set threshold values for stock items

ğŸ“§ Low Stock Notifications
Sends email alerts to admin when any stock item drops below its threshold (e.g. Pizza base < 20)

ğŸ“¸ Payment Flow
Instead of live payment gateway integration:

Users upload a screenshot of their transaction

Admin verifies and processes the order manually

ğŸ§° Tech Stack
Frontend	Backend	Database	Email Notifications
React.js	Node.js + Express.js	MongoDB	Nodemailer (Gmail)

